OL,3,CFreeview isn't going anywhere anytime
OL,4,Csoon but needs more HD channels
OL,6,GAnyone predicting the imminent death
OL,7,Gof terrestrial TV needs to think
OL,8,Gagain.
OL,10,FThe Culture Secretary Lucy Frazer
OL,11,Fmade it clear recently she had no
OL,12,Fintentions of allowing Freeview to be
OL,13,Fswitched off.
OL,15,FFor those commentators who'd
OL,16,Fmisinterpreted remarks by BBC
OL,17,FDirector General Tim Davy to mean the
OL,18,Fcorporation was truly heading for an
OL,19,F"internet only" future this may have
OL,20,Fbeen a surprise.
