OL,6,FIf would have forced consumers to
OL,7,Fchange equipment ` sometimes
OL,8,Funwillingly. For older people this
OL,9,Fmight have been confusing, for those
OL,10,Fon lower incomes it could have meant
OL,11,Fsacrifices.
OL,13,FIt will only be realistic to switch
OL,14,Foff Freeview if the point comes when
OL,15,Fthe service is being used by a tiny
OL,16,Fnumber of people.
OL,18,FIt will be very interesting to see
OL,19,Fwhether Freely ` the name for the new
OL,20,Fproduct designed to deliver linear TV
OL,21,Fover the internet ` takes off though.
