OL,6,FYou can certainly see the
OL,7,Fattractions. One compelling argument
OL,8,Fis it could provide the simplicity of
OL,9,Fan EPG but also include UHD and fully
OL,10,Fintegrated catch up services.
OL,12,FBut would this appeal to people
OL,13,Fwanting to upgrade from Freeview? Or
OL,14,Fwould it give some Freesat users the
OL,15,Fopportunity to junk their dish?
OL,17,FMuch will depend on how many people
OL,18,Fend up using the product.
