OL,6,FIt is easy to forget that some
OL,7,Ftechnological improvements have never
OL,8,Fflown commercially: quadrophonic
OL,9,Fsound on radio, BSB's picture
OL,10,Fquality, widescreen pictures on
OL,11,Fanalogue as attempted by Channel 4 in
OL,12,Fthe mid-90s. And do not even mention
OL,13,F3D television.
OL,15,FIt's also important not to presume
OL,16,Fthat any move to internet delivery
OL,17,Fmeans the end of linear services.
OL,18,FLinear services can also be provided
OL,19,Fonline ` indeed they are. Just look
OL,20,Fat the iPlayer or ITV X.
