OL,6,FBroadcasting is an asset for
OL,7,Feverybody in a country like the UK `
OL,8,Fnot merely a product for the
OL,9,Fcustomers of a particular service.
OL,11,FThe thought of the BBC pulling out of
OL,12,FFreeview in the foreseeable future
OL,13,Fwas always unrealistic.
OL,15,FIn a few months time, the BBC will
OL,16,Fstop providing separate programmes on
OL,17,FRadio 4 long wave.
OL,19,FHowever it is important to note that
OL,20,Fit has not yet announced when the
OL,21,FRadio 4 long wave transmitters will
OL,22,Fbe closed down.
